{"tid":1738640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"到場即查問姓朱女童位置 曾鈺成澄清非協助朱鎔基「孫女」離開校園","createTime":"2019-11-19T10:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T10:44:39.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2eb9628a9e4bdf9e315fdf744d4152fff44db844","tid":1738640,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:00:12.000Z","msg":"【理大攻防戰】到場即查問姓朱女童位置 曾鈺成澄清非協助朱鎔基「孫女」離開校園<br />\n<br />\n前立法會主席、民建聯曾鈺成昨晚聯同港大法律學者張達明等人進入理大校園，協助游說留守的未成年示威者理開，其中曾鈺成到場後查詢一名字「朱媛」在哪裡，其後親自陪同該女童離開，有指該女童後來消失於理大範圍，網上隨即有人質疑該名戴上黑超口罩離開的女童是官、政二代的後代，甚至有指是前國務院總理朱鎔基孫女、即香港金融發展局成員朱雲來的女兒。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，曾鈺成抵達理大校園後，便向「守護孩子」成員查詢是否有「朱媛」在校園內，獲告知有「嗰個女仔」，曾知悉後沒有再追問，並開始接受記者訪問。<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成透過助手回覆《蘋果》查詢時強調，昨日曾鈺成收到一名普通家長求助，其後到了理大協助被困人士離開，他澄清網傳受助的當事人並不是前國務院總理朱鎔基的任何親人，亦非任何達官貴人的子女，而為了保障當事人，他不會透露更多資料。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191119/60284034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60284034&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4Mqh1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=983f7357\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60284034&h=1222bc8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191119/60284034</a>"},{"pid":"78067467a48f49ed394afe023e2046690927646a","tid":1738640,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:02:52.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d00d0d9861a6e791c93d8b955473e83ec52a8aab","tid":1738640,"uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:04:40.000Z","msg":"曾生跟理大有咩關係？<br />\n曾生係議員？<br />\n曾生有咩官職？"},{"pid":"f137583aa2e3dcb551e819e8ee767c8bf9cf7526","tid":1738640,"uid":254594,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:08:17.000Z","msg":"掩飾唔到啦on9<br />\n唔係孫 唔通係私生女？"},{"pid":"05a7badd3144267dca4ffd24976a4aabcf9c0d37","tid":1738640,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"掩飾唔到啦on9<br />\n唔係孫 唔通係私生女？"},{"pid":"87982570b3a49ae12ae3a46c370b3f523f1445fb","tid":1738640,"uid":277912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"曾孫女?"},{"pid":"3735dd604d81e2ad5d8311132532df877ab77b61","tid":1738640,"uid":170160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"05a7badd3144267dca4ffd24976a4aabcf9c0d37","tid":1738640,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"掩飾唔到啦on9<br />\n唔係孫 唔通係私生女？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:10:52.000Z","msg":"有權有勢既人真係有私生子女唔出奇，就算窮 L 都好風流，申請綜援都好多人有兩頭住家 !"},{"pid":"b46aa531de3ab05144f75443ed24d3c6953bd50d","tid":1738640,"uid":326712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:13:14.000Z","msg":"皇族梗係唔係達官貴人<br />\n你話佢係達官貴人侮辱緊人地"},{"pid":"4377777b98ed9ff3317a1337693fed0301aa03ea","tid":1738640,"uid":175147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:27:45.000Z","msg":"朱媛係poly一役脫離暴動之名既重大棋子！係我地手足啊！"},{"pid":"02717d6b5f7f43dfca45ecd4e1daf4c657cbc2d2","tid":1738640,"uid":175147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:29:55.000Z","msg":"朱媛係poly一役脫離暴動之名既重大棋子！係我地手足啊！"},{"pid":"01701381b20d09669b1b033932ae3b92e3ca19de","tid":1738640,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:32:29.000Z","msg":"如果係普通市民個女，你會特別落場幫咩<br />\n欲蓋彌彰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e46a8706ff3d5a6b7cb9d26628aae704548b6f","tid":1738640,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:41:24.000Z","msg":"佢仲話朱女係弱智"},{"pid":"559560ea9c18035d0a07bde5f6dd0929c00f599c","tid":1738640,"uid":175147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45e46a8706ff3d5a6b7cb9d26628aae704548b6f","tid":1738640,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:41